Soak and cook @white beans{170%g}.

Sate @onion{1}, with @carrot{1} and @garlic{3%cloves}. Cover with water. Add @whole peppercorns{10}, @chilli flakes{} and some @salt.
Add @potatoes{2} cut into small cubes, @celery{2} and @tomato{2} cut into similar sizes. 
Ensure all is well covered and simmer for ~{15%min} or until tender. 

If desired, puree a third of the soup until smooth and add back into the pot. 

Serve with bread. 

This makes four portions, add more veggies if you want more soup.